temperatureDescription: Controls the randomness of outputs. Higher values make outputs more random, lower values make outputs more deterministic.
topPDescription: Controls the diversity of generated text. Lower values make the output more deterministic.
maxTokensDescription: Limits the maximum number of tokens the model can generate in a single interaction.
topKDescription: At each step, only considers the top K most probable tokens.
preventRepetitionPrompt: Make the model tend to generate new content rather than repeat what has already appeared.
reduceRepetition: Reduce the model's tendency to repeat the same words.
